    "description": "Join the AFL Logistics family as a Distribution Manager in Howrah. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout AFL Logistics:\nAFL Logistics is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Howrah, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with AFL Logistics!",
